Package: ScoMAP
Type: Package
Title: ScoMAP: Single-Cell Omics Mapping into spatial Axes using Pseudotemporal ordering
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2020-3-5
Author: Carmen Bravo González-Blas
Maintainer: Carmen Bravo González-Blas <carmen.bravogonzalezblas@kuleuven.vib.be>
Description: ScoMAP is an R package to spatially integrate single-cell omics data into virtual cells. These virtual cells may be organized on a template that resembles the tissue, or into an abstract space (e.g. when cell types are not spatially located). ScoMAP also includes functionalities to derive enhancer-to-gene relationships from the virtual template when mapping both single-cell transcriptomic and epigenomic data into the virtual cells.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Depends: R (>= 3.4)
biocViews: GenomicRanges, AnnotationDbi
